課程內容







			微波積體電路專題Special Topics on Microwaves Integrated Circuits

林坤佑   104下




課程概述

			1.固態微波元件及其非線性特性分析與模型 a.場效電晶體 b.雙極性電晶體 c.混頻與切換元件 d.混頻及倍頻元件 e.元件特性分析與模型 2.非線性微波電路之模擬與設計 a.功率放大器 b.混頻器 c.振盪器 d.倍頻器及其他電路 3.電路設計與佈局實作			

課程目標

			學習非線性微波積體電路理論與設計			

課程要求

			一、成績評量方式: 作業、考試及設計實作 二、預修課程: 微波單晶積體電路、電子學、電路學、電磁學

指定閱讀

			george d. vendelin, anthony m. pavio and ulrich l. rohde, microwave circuit design using linear and nonlinear techniques, john wiley & sons ltd., 1990.

參考書目

			[1] s. a. maas, microwave mixers, 2nd edition, artech house, norwood, ma, 1992.[2] f. ali and a. gupta, editors, hemts & hbts: devices, fabrication and circuits, artech house, norwood, ma, 1991.[3] r. goyal, editor, monolithic microwave integrated circuits: technology & design, artech house, norwood, ma, 1989.[4] inder bahl and prakash bhartia, microwave solid state circuit design, john wiley & sons ltd., 1988.[5] steve c. cripps, rf power amplifiers for wireless communications, artech house, norwood, ma, 1999.[6] david m. pozar, microwave engineering, 2nd edition, john wiley & sons ltd., 1998.[7] ulrich l. rohde and david p. newkirk, rf/microwave circuit design for wireless applications, john wiley & sons, inc., 2000.[8] edmar camargo, design of fet frequency multipliers and harmonic mixers, artech house, inc., norwood, ma, 1998.[9] 張盛富、張嘉展，無線通訊射頻晶片模組設計：射頻系統篇，全華圖書[10] 張盛富、張嘉展，無線通訊射頻晶片模組設計：射頻晶片篇，全華圖書

